sources.name: SourceDatasetBlobDog
sources.script:
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> SourceDatasetBlobDog

sources.name: DestinationDataset_fl7
sources.script:
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> DestinationDataset_fl7

typeProperties.script:
section Section1;
shared SourceDatasetBlobDog = let
  AdfDoc = AzureStorage.BlobContents("https://adfstoragecamilo.blob.core.windows.net/sql4dog/sqldog/dog.txt"),
  Csv = Csv.Document(AdfDoc, [Delimiter = ",", Encoding = TextEncoding.Utf8, QuoteStyle = QuoteStyle.Csv]),
  PromotedHeaders = Table.PromoteHeaders(Csv, [PromoteAllScalars = true])
in
  PromotedHeaders;
shared DestinationDataset_fl7 = let
  AdfDoc = Sql.Database("adfsqlservercamilo.database.windows.net", "ADFCamiloDatabase", [CreateNavigationProperties = false]),
  InputTable = AdfDoc{[Schema = "dbo", Item = "dog"]}[Data]
in
  InputTable;
shared UserQuery = let
  Source = SourceDatasetBlobDog
in
  Source;
